{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_02_01",
  "title": "小美山愛",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoir合宿後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "合宿お疲れ様。一緒に行けなくてすまなかったな\n特訓をしてみてどうだった？",
      "startTime": 7.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、手応えは十分です！\nライブではこれまでと違う私をお見せします！",
      "startTime": 12.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それはライブが楽しみだな。そういえば合宿中に\n愛が新しい振り付けを提案したそうじゃないか",
      "startTime": 20.033333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　『The Last Chance』です\n莉央さんと相談して振り付けを変えてみたんです",
      "startTime": 26,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "これでファンのみなさんに\nもっと楽しんでもらえると思います",
      "startTime": 31.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けを変えるのは大変だっただろ\nよく頑張ったな、愛",
      "startTime": 36.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい……ありがとうございます……",
      "startTime": 38.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "新しい振り付けは結構難しくて\nまだ納得のいくダンスが出来てないんですけど……",
      "startTime": 46.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "ライブまで時間はありますから\nもっと練習して本番までに完璧にしてみせます！",
      "startTime": 52.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "その意気だ。本番を楽しみにしてるぞ",
      "startTime": 56.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　期待を裏切らないように頑張ります！",
      "startTime": 59.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_coast_evening",
      "startTime": 64.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4……5、6、7、8……",
      "startTime": 65.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "動きにメリハリをつけて……\nここはもっとキレをよく出来るはず……",
      "startTime": 71.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。今日は愛しかいないのか？",
      "startTime": 76.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です！",
      "startTime": 80.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "みんなはもう練習を終えて帰りました\n私はもうちょっと振り付けの確認をしたかったので",
      "startTime": 86,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それで一人で居残り練習を？\n熱心なのはいいが、ちゃんと休憩は取ってるのか？",
      "startTime": 92.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "それが、つい時間を忘れて没頭しちゃって……",
      "startTime": 96.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "分かってはいるんですけど\n何もしてないと合宿で掴んだ感じを忘れそうで……",
      "startTime": 102.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちは分かるが\n今から休憩にして少し俺と話をしないか？",
      "startTime": 108.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 113.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、合宿中に莉央とパンケーキを食べたのか",
      "startTime": 114.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです！\nパンケーキを食べながらいろんな話をしたんですけど",
      "startTime": 120.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんの話を聞いて、私やこころに\nどれだけ期待してくれているか分かったんです",
      "startTime": 127.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "それで私も思いきって新しい振り付けを提案したら\n莉央さんはちゃんと受け止めてくれて……",
      "startTime": 134.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "その時に思ったんです\n遠慮なんかしてちゃダメなんだって",
      "startTime": 139.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "これからは私とこころがLizNoirを\n引っ張っていくんだって……",
      "startTime": 144.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "愛も頼もしくなったな。合宿に行く前とは別人のようだ",
      "startTime": 146.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですか？\nそういう風に見えたのなら嬉しいです",
      "startTime": 154.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私なんてまだまだです……",
      "startTime": 158.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai021.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの期待に応えられるように\nもっと努力しないと……",
      "startTime": 164.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……愛？",
      "startTime": 167.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai022.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いえ！　なんでもありません！",
      "startTime": 168.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……おっと、もうこんな時間か\n俺はそろそろ仕事に戻るけど、まだ練習を続けるのか？",
      "startTime": 175.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai023.m4a",
      "text": "はい、もう少しやっていきます",
      "startTime": 180,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ帰る時は声をかけてくれ\n無理せずにいい所で切り上げるんだぞ",
      "startTime": 185.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai024.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\nそれじゃあ私は練習に戻りますね",
      "startTime": 190.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-ai025.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、もっともっと頑張らないと！",
      "startTime": 192.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4500,
          "startTime": 197.36666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_02_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ライブに向けて気合が入ってるのはいいが\n少し心配だな……",
      "startTime": 200.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}